OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1778609471
OL,3,CMother domestically abused says court
OL,4,Chas allowed manipulation to continue
OL,6,FITV News Meridian's Oliver Hodges has
OL,7,Fbeen speaking to women who say the
OL,8,Ffamily court has allowed abuse from
OL,9,Ftheir ex-partners to continue
OL,11,FA mother who was the victim of
OL,12,Fdomestic abuse says the justice system
OL,13,Fhas allowed the manipulation she's
OL,14,Ffaced to continue.
OL,16,FShe is among a dozen women ITV News
OL,17,Fhas spoken to who say family
OL,18,Fcourtrooms, where custody rights of
OL,19,Fchildren are decided, are being used
OL,20,Fas weapons for abusers.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
