PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1778609471
OL,3,CMother domestically abused says court
OL,4,Chas allowed manipulation to continue
OL,6,FKate says her legal ordeal not only
OL,7,Fcost years of her life but also over a
OL,8,F#100,000, which resulted in her mother
OL,9,Fhaving to sell her home.
OL,11,FThe stress and torment continued
OL,12,Fdespite leaving the abusive
OL,13,Frelationship.
OL,15,F"He just wouldn't leave outside my
OL,16,Fhouse and - for hours and hours. Your
OL,17,Fhome becomes a prison.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
