OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1778609471
OL,3,CMother domestically abused says court
OL,4,Chas allowed manipulation to continue
OL,6,F"It's taken four years of my life and
OL,7,Fmy child's life - and we've now sat at
OL,8,Fcourt six times in total. Personally,
OL,9,FI would never go back to family court
OL,10,Fagain. It doesn't work.
OL,12,F"I'm under the threat of my
OL,13,Fabuser...with what the family courts
OL,14,Fhave done. And they have kept him
OL,15,Ffirmly in our life, but I will never
OL,16,Ftrust family court ever again."
OL,18,FAnother mother says she felt dismissed
OL,19,Fby judges even though her former
OL,20,Fpartner had been sent to prison.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
