OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1778609471
OL,3,CMother domestically abused says court
OL,4,Chas allowed manipulation to continue
OL,6,FSpeaking anonymously, Sophie says her
OL,7,Fchildren were forced into unsafe
OL,8,Fcontact with their father.
OL,10,F"Before the family court the last
OL,11,Fthing he said to me was that he wanted
OL,12,Fto kill me.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
