OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1778609471
OL,3,CMother domestically abused says court
OL,4,Chas allowed manipulation to continue
OL,6,F"I think I just assumed that I was
OL,7,Fgoing to be able to explain the full
OL,8,Fhistory and I would get the same jaw
OL,9,Fdrop response I'd had from other
OL,10,Fpeople and professionals - and they
OL,11,Fwere gonna go 'wow this guy's
OL,12,Fdangerous, we need to keep these
OL,13,Fchildren safe'...and most of it isn't
OL,14,Fheard, most of it is disregarded."
OL,16,F"I've got friends that I'm aware that
OL,17,Fwon't leave their abusive partners
OL,18,Fbecause the situation they're in, they
OL,19,Fknow they have a way to manage. And I
OL,20,Fthink they've seen how much of a
OL,21,Fbattle it's been for me."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
