PN,41106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1778609471
OL,3,CMother domestically abused says court
OL,4,Chas allowed manipulation to continue
OL,6,FJudges often order parents to use co-
OL,7,Fparenting apps, but these are used as
OL,8,Fanother form of control allowing
OL,9,Fabusive partners to send un-true
OL,10,Fallegations such as accusing mothers
OL,11,Fof 'poisoning their children'.
OL,13,FCharities such as Stop Domestic Abuse
OL,14,Fsay they regularly hear from people
OL,15,Fworried about the process of going to
OL,16,Fcourt.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
