OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1778609471
OL,3,CMother domestically abused says court
OL,4,Chas allowed manipulation to continue
OL,6,FCEO Claire Lambon said the cycle of
OL,7,Fabuse can continue, "We see year on,
OL,8,Fevery year an increase in demand for
OL,9,Four services. And we have had many
OL,10,Fcases where the survivor in court has
OL,11,Freally had an anxious time because
OL,12,Fthey've come face to face with the
OL,13,Fabuser.
OL,15,F"The court case can be another weapon
OL,16,Fin perpetuating abuse."
OL,18,FFamily court barrister Dr Charlotte
OL,19,FProudman said, "Many think of the
OL,20,Ffamily court I think now as being a
OL,21,Fplayground for domestic abuse.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41108
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1778609471
OL,3,CMother domestically abused says court
OL,4,Chas allowed manipulation to continue
OL,6,F"And arguably things have got worse in
OL,7,Ffact over the last ten years I would
OL,8,Fsay and that's because of this notion
OL,9,Fof parental alienation which has
OL,10,Fstarted to gain huge amounts of
OL,11,Ftraction and power in family courts."
OL,13,FThe Ministry of Justice told us, "It
OL,14,Fis unacceptable for anyone to use the
OL,15,Ffamily courts to further distress
OL,16,Fvictims, which is why we are driving
OL,17,Fthrough reforms to give survivors
OL,18,Fearlier specialist support,
OL,19,Fstrengthening safeguards and shutting
OL,20,Fdown attempts to use the system as a
OL,21,Ftool of ongoing control.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
