OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1778609471
OL,3,CMother domestically abused says court
OL,4,Chas allowed manipulation to continue
OL,6,F"This includes requiring courts to
OL,7,Fconsider special measures - such as
OL,8,Fprotective screens or giving evidence
OL,9,Fby video link - to enable victims to
OL,10,Ffully participate in proceedings."
OL,12,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,13,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,14,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,15,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,16,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,17,Fbelow...
